{"type":"message","id":"817448ab","parentId":"4859013b","timestamp":"2026-04-01T07:50:34.837Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_e5y9b6gfydgc57wvho1sb4so","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"memory/2026-04-01.md","content":"\n\n## 2026-04-01 Whisper 文本提取任务\n\n用户请求：使用 Whisper 从 fulai_mountain.mp4 视频中提取文本\n\n### 过程记录\n\n1. 确认视频文件存在于当前工作目录\n2. 检查发现 whisper 未安装，使用 pip3 安装 openai-whisper，安装成功\n3. 初始选择 large 模型下载，遇到 SHA256 校验和不匹配错误\n4. 切换为 medium 模型重新下载，下载成功\n5. 执行转录命令，成功提取文本\n\n### 结果\n\n- 提取文本：`中文字幕组`\n- 输出文件：`fulai_mountain.txt`\n- 最终使用模型：medium（中文）\n\n### 经验教训\n\n- large 模型下载容易出错且速度慢，medium 模型体积小一半，下载更快更稳定\n- 对于短视频，medium 模型精度足够\n"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"custom-ark-cn-beijing-volces-com","model":"ark-code-latest","usage":{"input":11632,"output":263,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":11895,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775029817821,"responseId":"021775029818182b686cf77507a74aa4905f351832e6617ced3da"}}
